FROM store_sales AS ss
JOIN store AS s
  ON s.s_store_sk = ss.ss_store_sk
JOIN customer_demographics AS cd
  ON cd.cd_demo_sk = ss.ss_cdemo_sk
JOIN household_demographics AS hd
  ON ss.ss_hdemo_sk = hd.hd_demo_sk
JOIN customer_address AS ca
  ON ss.ss_addr_sk = ca.ca_address_sk
JOIN date_dim AS d
  ON ss.ss_sold_date_sk = d.d_date_sk
JOIN demographic_filter AS df
  ON ss.ss_hdemo_sk = df.ss_hdemo_sk
  AND ss.ss_cdemo_sk = df.ss_cdemo_sk
  AND ss.ss_sales_price = df.ss_sales_price
JOIN address_filter AS af
  ON ss.ss_addr_sk = af.ss_addr_sk AND ss.ss_net_profit = af.ss_net_profit

  d.d_year = 2001
  AND (
    (
      cd.cd_marital_status = 'D'
      AND cd.cd_education_status = 'Unknown'
      AND hd.hd_dep_count = 3
    )

      cd.cd_marital_status = 'S'

    )

      AND cd.cd_education_status = '4 yr Degree'

    (

SELECT
  AVG(ss_quantity) AS avg_ss_quantity, /* Combine all conditions using OR logic (original query had OR between all combinations) */
  AVG(ss_ext_sales_price) AS avg_ss_ext_sales_price,
  AVG(ss_ext_wholesale_cost) AS avg_ss_ext_wholesale_cost,
  SUM(ss_ext_wholesale_cost) AS sum_ss_ext_wholesale_cost
FROM (
  SELECT
    COALESCE(
      avg_qty_cond1,
      avg_qty_cond2,
      avg_qty_cond3,
      avg_qty_cond4,
      avg_qty_cond5,
      avg_qty_cond6,
      avg_qty_cond7,
      avg_qty_cond8,
      avg_qty_cond9
    ) AS ss_quantity,
    COALESCE(
      avg_sales_cond1,
      avg_sales_cond2,
      avg_sales_cond3,
      avg_sales_cond4,
      avg_sales_cond5,
      avg_sales_cond6,
      avg_sales_cond7,
      avg_sales_cond8,
      avg_sales_cond9
    ) AS ss_ext_sales_price,
    COALESCE(
      avg_cost_cond1,
      avg_cost_cond2,
      avg_cost_cond3,
      avg_cost_cond4,
      avg_cost_cond5,
      avg_cost_cond6,
      avg_cost_cond7,
      avg_cost_cond8,
      avg_cost_cond9
    ) AS ss_ext_wholesale_cost,
    COALESCE(
      sum_cost_cond1,
      sum_cost_cond2,
      sum_cost_cond3,
      sum_cost_cond4,
      sum_cost_cond5,
      sum_cost_cond6,
      sum_cost_cond7,
      sum_cost_cond8,
      sum_cost_cond9
    ) AS ss_ext_wholesale_cost_sum
  FROM combined_scan
  CROSS JOIN (VALUES
    (1),
    (2),
    (3),
    (4),
    (5),
    (6),
    (7),
    (8),
    (9)) AS conditions(n)
  WHERE
    (
      n = 1 AND NOT avg_qty_cond1 IS NULL
    )
    OR (
      n = 2 AND NOT avg_qty_cond2 IS NULL

    OR (
      n = 3 AND NOT avg_qty_cond3 IS NULL

    )
